response.overview: A mélange of 50s and 60s clips lead off this collection, complete with zebra stripes, big hair, and sombreros, capped by an itsy-bitsy polka dot bikini strip in Taffeta Tease. The focus turns to the great outdoors as William H. Door contributes a pair of travel films, Switzerland and Hawaii, and then fine outdoor dramas featuring Joanne Arnold and Bobbie Reynolds—watch out for those yuccas! Aqua Nudes Real chips in poolside pulchritude, followed by two distinctively different loops that pose a beautiful blonde dramatically atop a windswept rock. In Hollywood Beauties Reel No. 4 we get a rare full color glimpse of the “canyon” genre. Stacy Randall takes a relaxing shower as the 1950s end, and we finish up with five gyrating, lip-licking early 60s gals bidding us adieu.
response.title: Nudie Cuties: Volume 8
